---
---
<section class="section-sm">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-in">
      <div class="badge mb-5">Personality</div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-text-primary tracking-tight mb-5">
        Talks like a <span class="text-cal-gold">Bear</span>,<br/>not a bot.
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 fade-in">
        <div class="card border-border/30 opacity-60">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-medium text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Generic AI</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted italic">&ldquo;I'd be happy to help you check your assignments. Let me look into that for you.&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-medium text-text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">OpenMind</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">&ldquo;You've got 3 things due this week &#x1f4da; NLP midterm is the big one &mdash; 30% of your grade. I'd start there.&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
        <div class="card border-border/30 opacity-60">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-medium text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Generic AI</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted italic">&ldquo;I notice you have an assignment with an approaching deadline. Shall I set a reminder?&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="text-[10px] font-medium text-text-primary uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">OpenMind</div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary">&ldquo;&warning; bro that writing prompt is due TOMORROW 11:59pm. Have you started?&rdquo;</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="text-center text-text-muted text-xs max-w-md mx-auto leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      References Moffitt, Doe, Main Stacks, Free Speech Caf&eacute;, Croads. Says &ldquo;hella.&rdquo; Celebrates with &ldquo;Fiat Lux!&rdquo; Might shade Stanford. &#x1f43b;
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
